Certain items, most notably motors, are *significantly* cheaper than Pitsco
if you order them through the LEGO shop-at-home catalog (1-800-453-4652).

If you are ordering for an educational instititution and if you ask the
shop-at-home people, you can get an additional 10-15% discount.

